  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"template-hero download-center-hero\">\n<div class=\"container template-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"template-hero-copy\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb download-breadcrumb\">\n<a href=\"/resources\">\n              资源中心\n            </a>\n<span>/</span>\n<b>下载中心</b>\n</div>\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">\n            DOWNLOAD CENTER\n          </span>\n<h1>工程资料与制造模板下载</h1>\n<p>\n            面向研发、采购、质量和项目管理团队，整理精密零部件报价沟通、\n            DFM 审查、材料选型、图纸规范、质量验收和交付资料所需的标准化文件。\n            通过统一资料模板，减少前期沟通遗漏，提高报价和项目推进效率。\n          </p>\n<div class=\"download-hero-actions\">\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#download-list\">\n              浏览下载资料\n            </a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/resources/faq\">\n              查看常见问题\n            </a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"template-hero-panel\">\n<img alt=\"工程资料与制造模板下载\" src=\"/precision/insight-knowledge.jpg\"/>\n<div class=\"template-panel-row\">\n<strong>Templates</strong>\n<span>报价与项目资料模板</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"template-panel-row\">\n<strong>Checklists</strong>\n<span>DFM、质量与交付检查清单</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"template-panel-row\">\n<strong>Guides</strong>\n<span>材料、工艺与设计规范资料</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"template-section download-overview-section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"download-overview-layout\">\n<article class=\"download-overview-card is-primary\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">\n              DOCUMENT SYSTEM\n            </span>\n<h2>让报价、设计评审与验收资料更标准</h2>\n<p>\n              下载中心覆盖从项目前期报价到后期验收交付的关键资料，\n              帮助您快速准备图纸、模型、材料要求、公差说明、表面处理要求和质量文件需求。\n            </p>\n<a href=\"#download-list\">\n              查看全部资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">→</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<div class=\"download-overview-grid\">\n<div>\n<b>01</b>\n<strong>报价资料准备</strong>\n<span>提交图纸、模型、数量、材料、表面处理和交期要求。</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<b>02</b>\n<strong>DFM 设计审查</strong>\n<span>提前检查壁厚、公差、圆角、深腔、装夹和刀具可达性。</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<b>03</b>\n<strong>质量验收文件</strong>\n<span>统一首件检测、尺寸记录、材料证明和出货验收资料。</span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<b>04</b>\n<strong>材料工艺参考</strong>\n<span>对照材料性能、加工限制、表面处理和成本差异。</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"template-section soft download-list-section\" id=\"download-list\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"download-section-head\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">\n              DOWNLOAD FILES\n            </span>\n<h2>资料下载</h2>\n<p>\n              按报价、设计、材料、质量和交付场景筛选所需资料。\n              下方下载链接目前使用占位文件路径，正式上线时替换为真实 PDF、XLSX 或 DOCX 文件地址即可。\n            </p>\n</div>\n<a class=\"resource-section-entry\" href=\"/about#contact\">\n            没找到需要的资料？\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"download-toolbar\">\n<label class=\"download-search\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n<circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></circle>\n<path d=\"M20 20l-4.3-4.3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path>\n</svg>\n<input aria-label=\"搜索下载资料\" id=\"download-search-input\" placeholder=\"搜索资料、模板或关键词...\" type=\"search\"/>\n</label>\n<div aria-label=\"下载资料分类\" class=\"download-filter-list\" role=\"group\">\n<button aria-pressed=\"true\" class=\"download-filter-button active\" data-download-filter=\"all\" type=\"button\">\n              全部\n            </button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"download-filter-button\" data-download-filter=\"quote\" type=\"button\">\n              报价资料\n            </button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"download-filter-button\" data-download-filter=\"design\" type=\"button\">\n              设计规范\n            </button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"download-filter-button\" data-download-filter=\"material\" type=\"button\">\n              材料工艺\n            </button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"download-filter-button\" data-download-filter=\"quality\" type=\"button\">\n              质量验收\n            </button>\n<button aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"download-filter-button\" data-download-filter=\"delivery\" type=\"button\">\n              交付资料\n            </button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"download-result-status\">\n<span id=\"download-result-count\">共 9 份资料</span>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"download-grid\" id=\"download-grid\">\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"quote\" data-download-keywords=\"报价 清单 图纸 模型 数量 材料 表面处理 交期\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>QUOTE</span>\n<b>PDF</b>\n</div>\n<h3>报价资料准备清单</h3>\n<p>\n              整理提交报价前需要准备的 3D 模型、二维图纸、材料、数量、\n              表面处理、关键公差和交期信息，帮助快速完成加工评估。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：采购 / 研发</span>\n<span>约 2 页</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/quote-preparation-checklist.pdf\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"design\" data-download-keywords=\"DFM 可制造性 检查 清单 壁厚 圆角 公差 装夹 深腔\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>DFM</span>\n<b>PDF</b>\n</div>\n<h3>DFM 可制造性检查表</h3>\n<p>\n              覆盖 CNC 零件常见的壁厚、圆角、深槽、倒扣、公差、\n              装夹基准和刀具可达性检查项，适合投产前快速自查。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：结构设计 / 工艺</span>\n<span>约 4 页</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/dfm-review-checklist.pdf\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"design\" data-download-keywords=\"工程图纸 标注 尺寸 公差 粗糙度 螺纹 技术要求\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>DRAWING</span>\n<b>PDF</b>\n</div>\n<h3>工程图纸标注规范参考</h3>\n<p>\n              汇总二维工程图中尺寸基准、孔位、螺纹、表面粗糙度、\n              形位公差和技术要求的常见表达方式，减少图纸歧义。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：研发 / 设计</span>\n<span>约 6 页</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/engineering-drawing-guideline.pdf\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"material\" data-download-keywords=\"材料 参数 铝合金 不锈钢 钛合金 碳钢 工程塑料\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>MATERIAL</span>\n<b>XLSX</b>\n</div>\n<h3>常用材料参数对照表</h3>\n<p>\n              对比铝合金、不锈钢、钛合金、碳钢、铜材和工程塑料的密度、\n              强度、耐腐蚀、切削性能和典型应用场景。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：选材 / 采购</span>\n<span>表格文件</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/material-parameter-comparison.xlsx\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"material\" data-download-keywords=\"表面处理 阳极氧化 电镀 喷涂 钝化 发黑 抛光 膜厚\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>FINISH</span>\n<b>PDF</b>\n</div>\n<h3>表面处理选型表</h3>\n<p>\n              梳理阳极氧化、电镀、喷涂、钝化、发黑、抛光等工艺的适用材料、\n              外观效果、膜厚范围和典型使用场景。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：外观 / 防腐</span>\n<span>约 5 页</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/surface-finishing-selection.pdf\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"quality\" data-download-keywords=\"首件 检测 报告 FAI 尺寸 质量 检验\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>QUALITY</span>\n<b>XLSX</b>\n</div>\n<h3>首件检测报告模板</h3>\n<p>\n              用于记录首件尺寸、公差、检测工具、实测值、判定结果和确认签字，\n              适合样品试制和批量投产前的质量确认。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：质量 / 生产</span>\n<span>表格文件</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/first-article-inspection-template.xlsx\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"quality\" data-download-keywords=\"批量 验收 抽检 终检 材质证明 检测报告 出货\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>INSPECTION</span>\n<b>PDF</b>\n</div>\n<h3>批量验收资料清单</h3>\n<p>\n              整理批量订单出货时常见的材质证明、尺寸检测记录、表面处理报告、\n              CMM 报告、包装清单和交付文件要求。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：质检 / 采购</span>\n<span>约 3 页</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/batch-inspection-document-list.pdf\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"quote\" data-download-keywords=\"3D 模型 STEP IGES STL OBJ 格式 转换 上传\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>MODEL</span>\n<b>PDF</b>\n</div>\n<h3>3D 模型格式提交规范</h3>\n<p>\n              说明 STEP、IGES、STL、OBJ 等常见三维格式的适用场景，\n              以及提交模型时需要注意的单位、比例、版本和特征完整性。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：研发 / 模型提交</span>\n<span>约 3 页</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/3d-model-submission-guideline.pdf\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n<article class=\"download-card\" data-download-category=\"delivery\" data-download-keywords=\"项目 需求 说明 模板 工况 数量 交期 包装 物流\">\n<div class=\"download-card-top\">\n<span>PROJECT</span>\n<b>DOCX</b>\n</div>\n<h3>项目需求说明模板</h3>\n<p>\n              用于统一描述零件使用工况、装配关系、载荷需求、材料偏好、\n              数量阶段、交期节点、包装和物流要求。\n            </p>\n<div class=\"download-card-meta\">\n<span>适用：项目 / 采购</span>\n<span>文档模板</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"download-card-action\" download=\"\" href=\"/downloads/project-requirement-template.docx\">\n              下载资料\n              <i aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</i>\n</a>\n</article>\n</div>\n<div class=\"download-empty-state\" hidden=\"\" id=\"download-empty-state\">\n<strong>暂未找到相关资料</strong>\n<span>请尝试更换分类或搜索其他关键词。</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"template-section download-process-section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"template-section-head\">\n<span class=\"template-kicker\">\n            HOW TO USE\n          </span>\n<h2>如何使用这些下载资料？</h2>\n<p>\n            建议在项目沟通前完成资料准备，尤其是报价、DFM 审查和质量验收相关文件。\n          </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"download-process-grid\">\n<article>\n<b>01</b>\n<h3>报价前准备</h3>\n<p>\n              下载报价资料准备清单，整理图纸、模型、数量、材料和表面处理要求。\n            </p>\n</article>\n<article>\n<b>02</b>\n<h3>设计前自查</h3>\n<p>\n              使用 DFM 检查表和图纸标注规范，提前识别壁厚、公差和装夹风险。\n            </p>\n</article>\n<article>\n<b>03</b>\n<h3>材料工艺比对</h3>\n<p>\n              对照材料参数和表面处理表，确认零件性能、成本和加工可行性。\n            </p>\n</article>\n<article>\n<b>04</b>\n<h3>质量交付确认</h3>\n<p>\n              使用首件报告模板和验收资料清单，明确检测文件和出货资料要求。\n            </p>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"cta-band\">\n<div class=\"container cta-inner\">\n<div><h2>资料准备完成后，需要进一步评估加工方案？</h2>\n<p> 上传图纸、模型和项目需求，获取材料、工艺、报价和交期建议。</p>\n</div>\n<a class=\"light-btn\" href=\"/quote?mode=quickQuote#quote-upload\">立即报价</a>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
}
